name: Paparazzi
description: With this preset you can achieve an expressive look with sharp light and rich contrasted shadows. The way to go to make your portraits stand out from the crowd.

name: Purple Rain
description: A visionary preset to give a purple touch to all your scenes. All pinks and violets shades brighten up and stand out. Macro shots will gain a magic soul with this lavender overlay.

name: Heavenly Blue
description: The best preset to lighten up the blue of your skies and seas. All cold shades acquire a bright and deep hue. Shots become sharper and clearer, and everything will appear so refreshing.

name: Fluffy Friends
description: The warmest preset to make your pets even cuter than what they are. Brown and all shades of fur gain in texture and warm tones. Cats and dogs photos will instantly have a softer look.

name: Pumpkin Spice
description: A full orange preset to give your pumpkins a richer and enhanced look. All orange shades stand out thanks to a balanced contrast and richer shadows. All pumpkin related shots become memorable.

name: Autumn Vibes
description: A fall preset to brighten all your orange and red tones. All falls and trees red tones will be enhanced by a richer contrast. Autumn shots will appear more intense and texturized.

name: So Fifties
description: A vintage preset perfect to give your pics a retro style. All colors lose saturation and contrast. Portrait and objects grow a greener overlay to copycat the film photos.

name: Venice Painter
description: A colorful preset designed to enhance the shiny tones of Italian cities. The entire rainbow palette becomes brighter and more vibrant. Wall paintings and all dyes take the best advantage.

name: Toujours Paris
description: The moodiest preset to give your city pics the Parisian look. Grey and black shades get instantly darker and high-contrast. Landscapes and skies gain a romantic rainy mood.

name: Blogger Interior
description: The ideal preset to make a cool interior look even more stylish. All colors are defined and shine out without being edgy. Furniture and objects appear as the latest trend essentials.

name: Neon
description: The best preset to give a twist to your night photos. All colours gain a blue and red tone. Shots become darker and mysterious with a glowing touch.

name: Urban Portrait
description: A stylish preset designed to enhance the coolness of your portraits. Faces, clothes and backgrounds are desatured and over exposed. Everything has a strong street style photography mood.

name: Amber Light
description: A warm preset to give a magic touch to your pics. Yellow and orange shades get warmer and deeper. Coffee, red hair and wooden become instantly intense.

name: Fields Of Gold
description: A golden preset to make blonde hair shine and glow. All yellow tones are enriched and the atmosphere is warmed up by a golden hour effect.

name: Rum And Cigars
description: A colorful preset to brighten up all Cuban shades. Colors deepen and strengthen, matter becomes strong and solid. Retro car and tinted house will gain good contrast.

name: Cozy Sunday
description: The coziest preset to make your interior more “hygge”. Warm tones and a soft light brighten up your home photos in a flash.

name: Houseplant Lover
description: The greenest preset ideal to make your houseplants pop out. Green shades gain in saturation and leaves become more textured. Use this filter in all interior pics with green plants.

name: Pinky Blinders
description: The most pinkish preset to give a magenta touch to your pics. All pink flowers, fruits or tissues will stand out and become protagonist.

name: Scent Of Bread
description: The best preset to enhance your homemade baked bread. All beige and brown shades become warmer and more appetizing. More contrast and texture emphasize the effect.

name: Eat Your Greens
description: The ideal preset  to enhance the your veggie dishes. All vegetables and fruits colors gain in luminance and saturation. Food photos become cooler and brighter at the same time.

name: Real Leather
description: A warm preset to enhance the texture and colors of real leather goods. Brown and orange shades get warmer and darker. Boots, gloves and bags gain instantly a luxury appeal.

name: Snowball Effect
description: A bright preset to make your winter pics stand out. Snow whites are enriched and the atmosphere is cooled by a winter light effect.

name: Yellow To Orange
description: A color focus preset to transform all your yellow details into red. All tints from lemons to taxis will turn into a reddish shade.

name: Lights Up
description: The most enlightened preset to brighten up your portraits with a glam look. Colors lose saturation and gain in contrast to emphasize the style of the subject.

name: Sunshine
description: The ideal preset to enlighten your seaside pics. All blues and turquoise shades become brighter and stronger.

name: Celebrity Skin
description: The best preset to make your portraits flawless yet vibrant. All skin tones become peachy and bright, for an instant healthy looking effect.

name: Orange Shades
description: A vitamin C booster for all your food photos containing orange elements. Orange hues gain in richness and contrast to become the focus of the pic.

name: Wild Nature
description: A wild preset to make your nature photos stand out. All green shades are intensified and the atmosphere is darkened and dense.

name: Blue To Green
description: A color focus preset to transform all your blue details into green. All tints from dark blue to light blue will turn into an aquamarine tint.

name: Back To The 80s
description: A vintage preset to make your photos a back to the 80s look. Colors lose in saturation and gain a sepia shade, while the texture is less marked.

name: Drama Portrait
description: The coolest preset ideal to make your portraits stand out. All tinted shades lose in saturation and gain in contrast. Use this filter for all epic mood photos.

name: Cozy Interior
description: The coziest preset to give a cool touch to your interior pics. Warm shades, rich contrasts and stand out whites will give your apartment a magazine style look.

name: Golden Hour
description: A warm preset to intensify your golden hour shots. All natural tints become reddish while gaining in contrast and exposure.

name: Fairy Tale
description: A dreamy preset to give a magical touch to your outdoor photos. All colors are desaturated and a white layer gives an enchanted atmosphere to the landscape.

name: XMas Lights
description: The best preset to enhance your Christmas pics with red details. All green and brown shades become darker and more intense. Luminance and saturation emphasize the red shades.

name: Into The Wild
description: The ideal preset to enhance your pics of traveling in the nature. All the natural tones are desaturated while bodies and faces stand out.

name: Buon Appetito
description: The best preset to enhance your food pics details. All yellow, green and red colors become brighter and more intense. Luminance and saturation emphasize all natural elements.

name: Cold Weather
description: The coolest preset ideal to enhance your winter pics. All colors lose in temperature and gain a blueish shade.

name: Intense Portrait
description: The deepest preset to make your portraits stand out. All tinted shades gain in saturation and contrast. Use this filter to intensify your portrait photos.

name: Hygge Moments
description: The coziest preset to give a relaxing touch to your interior pics. Warm shades and soft contrasts will give your chilling moments a danish style look.

name: Girl On Fire
description: A warm preset to intensify your portrait shots. All natural tints become warmer while gaining in contrast and decreasing in exposure.

name: Black Coffee
description: The best preset to enhance your breakfast coffee pics. All black coffee and cappuccino shades become more intense. Luminance and saturation emphasize the cozy moment.

name: Meditation
description: The most stylish preset to enhance your travel pics. All the natural tones are desaturated and gain in contrast and highlights.
